content: DESCRIPTIONIt seems that this is the most attractive and simple company at the moment. We are launching it to promote the newly created RIA project discord server, this company will later become part of a full-fledged company.Our main advantage is that this is not a one-day project, but a very promising and developing project, all the advantages of which you can find on our official website.The main task of the participant is communication and development of the discord server and the project as a whole. As you communicate and participate in the life of the project, your role of on the discord server will grow and you will be entitled to a percentage of the RIA COMMUNITY BANK monthly payment (check #bank channel on the server), which replenished every month. Minimim bank amount 100 RIA.Thus, the higher your role on the server, the larger the payout you will receive EVERY MONTHBounty company will be closed after reaching 1000 membersRules 1. You must join the Discord channel: https://discord.gg/XHjPKHABYK2. You should not just write messages, but conduct a dialogue with the participants of the project Discord channel.3. You are not allowed to write a message about the bounty campaign in the chat4. You should not have the name of another project in the profile name5. Participants are prohibited from using any hashtags in the Discord channel!Three easy steps1. Fill spreadsheet2. Proof of registration3. Increase your role on the aRIA discord server and receive monthly paymentsSpreadsheetProof Of Registration Post Format:Code:#PROOF OF REGISTRATIONForum Username:Forum Profile Link:
